	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				The info for the poison vials is:<BR>
Poison vial = vial sketch, small block of clay, flask of water, and an animal pelt. (Zombie skin work best sense they stack, Ruined pelts do not work.)<BR>
Lined poison vial = lined vial sketch, small block of clay, water flask, and animal pelt.<BR>
<BR>
Sealed vials are currently broken. I would still recommend getting the potter book for this might change.<BR>
You should have at least 120 in pottery before trying these; I would recommend 128, to save a little cash.<BR>

				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
