			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Ok first I really did not feel like reading through the 8 pages on the other thing so I came here hoping to answer some questions.  To the person who asked what they should make after large jars, well make medium bowls.  They will carry you to something like 111 skill or somewhere around there.  And if it was not posted in those 8 pages, to make the Deity of Protection you need to combine in a pottery wheel:  Small deity sketch, Block of Clay (not small or large, medium), Water flask, and a Carnelian.  The Carnelian is a jewl, that costs about 1plat.<BR>
Well hope this helps.<BR>
<BR>
Kainne<BR>
18th level Iksar Monk of Pain<BR>
Tribunal
